                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 1v (above):  The righteous ones enter this gate and the sinners are looking for it.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 143ra (ls.1-10): Note on the commissioner and supplication prayer.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 143ra (ls.1-10): The one who caused this Vita be written (is) Habtä Śǝllase, having great hope in the prayer of Mary, the Mother of Alfa, so that he might take the blessing of Saul and "Stone". And for me, and for Zena Gäbrǝˀel who wrote it (the book), she will be a protection. Forever and ever. Amen.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#"/>
                           <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 143ra (l.12-20-rb): If this (book) of the Vitae of the twelve Apostles has been robbed or brought out of the place of Mary, be it by a priest or a deacon or a governor, I, Habtä Sǝllase, priest and monk, excommunicate (him) through the rope of Peter and Paul, pillars of the world, which will not be loosened, through the mouth of the Prophets and Apostles, the mouth of the metropolitan, tongues of the fire, through Michael and Gabriel and Kirubiel, the mouth of Mary, Mother of God. May it be tied in the heaven and on the earth. For eternity, amen.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- A short note, partly unreadable: ዕቀባ፡ [sic?] ሥላሴ፡ ወሐይለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወከፍለ፡ [n.l.]ም፡  ፍቁራንየ፡  "ʿƎquba Śǝllase and Ḥaylä Śǝllase and Kǝflä ... (are) my beloved ones"</item>
                     </list>
